            response speed, or intake completion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <ol class="mt-12 grid gap-0 border-t border-[#1c2333] lg:grid-cols-4 lg:border-t-0">
          {rollout.map((item, idx) => (
            <li class="relative border-b border-[#1c2333] py-7 transition duration-300 hover:bg-[#0c111c]/45 lg:border-b-0 lg:border-l lg:px-6 lg:py-0 lg:first:border-l-0">
              <div class="hidden h-px w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#1c2333] to-transparent lg:block"></div>
              <div class="lg:pt-7">
                <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
                  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#67e8f9]/85">{item.step}</span>
                  {idx < rollout.length - 1 ? <span class="hidden h-px flex-1 bg-[#1c2333] lg:block" aria-hidden="true"></span> : null}
                </div>
                <h3 class="mt-3 text-[16px] font-medium tracking-tight text-[#f5f7fb]">{item.title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-[13.5px] leading-relaxed text-[#8a93a6]">{item.body}</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class={`${CONTAINER} grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.72fr_1.28fr] lg:gap-20`}>
        <div>
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#67e8f9]/85">FAQ</span>
          <h2 class="mt-4 text-[clamp(1.9rem,3.4vw,2.7rem)] font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#f5f7fb]">
            Practical questions before the first healthcare AI workflow.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-[#1c2333]">
          {faq.map((item) => (
            <section class="border-b border-[#1c2333] py-6">
              <h3 class="text-[16px] font-medium tracking-tight text-[#f5f7fb]">{item.q}</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-[14.5px] leading-relaxed text-[#8a93a6]">{item.a}</p>
            </section>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="border-t border-[#1c2333] bg-[#0a0e17] py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class={`${CONTAINER} grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] lg:gap-20`}>
        <div>
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#67e8f9]/85">Contact</span>
          <h2 class="mt-4 text-[clamp(1.9rem,3.4vw,2.7rem)] font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#f5f7fb]">
            Book a healthcare workflow review.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-md text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[#8a93a6]">
            Share your care setting, current systems, request volume, and the administrative workflow you want to improve first.
            We will help define a supervised workflow with clear handoff and review rules.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 text-[14px] text-[#c8d0de]">
            {reviewTakeaways.map((text, index) => {
              const Icon = index === 0 ? PackageCheck : index === 1 ? Search : ShieldCheck;
              return (
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <Icon class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-[#67e8f9]" stroke-width={1.6} />
                  <span>{text}</span>
                </div>
              );
            })}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-[14px] text-[#c8d0de]">
            <Mail class="h-4 w-4 text-[#67e8f9]" stroke-width={1.6} />
            <a href={`mailto:${brandEmail}`} class="border-b border-[#1c2333] pb-0.5 transition hover:border-[#67e8f9]/60 hover:text-[#f5f7fb]">
              {brandEmail}
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <form
          id="healthcare-inquiry-form"
          class="rounded-2xl border border-[#1c2333] bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0c111c] to-[#0a0e17] p-6 shadow-[0_30px_90px_-60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.9)] sm:p-7"
        >
          <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <span class="flex h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#34d399] pulse-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#c8d0de]">
              healthcare workflow review
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <label class="grid gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#8a93a6]">
              Name
              <input required name="name" class="h-11 w-full rounded-md border border-[#1c2333] bg-[#0c111c] px-3.5 text-[14px] text-[#f5f7fb] outline-none transition placeholder:text-[#5e6678] focus:border-[#67e8f9]/60 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#67e8f9]/15" placeholder="Your name" />
            </label>
            <label class="grid gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#8a93a6]">
              Work email
              <input required type="email" name="email" class="h-11 w-full rounded-md border border-[#1c2333] bg-[#0c111c] px-3.5 text-[14px] text-[#f5f7fb] outline-none transition placeholder:text-[#5e6678] focus:border-[#67e8f9]/60 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#67e8f9]/15" placeholder="you@clinic.com" />
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <label class="grid gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#8a93a6]">
              Organization
              <input required name="organization" class="h-11 w-full rounded-md border border-[#1c2333] bg-[#0c111c] px-3.5 text-[14px] text-[#f5f7fb] outline-none transition placeholder:text-[#5e6678] focus:border-[#67e8f9]/60 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#67e8f9]/15" placeholder="Clinic or practice name" />
            </label>
            <label class="grid gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#8a93a6]">
              Care setting
              <input name="setting" class="h-11 w-full rounded-md border border-[#1c2333] bg-[#0c111c] px-3.5 text-[14px] text-[#f5f7fb] outline-none transition placeholder:text-[#5e6678] focus:border-[#67e8f9]/60 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#67e8f9]/15" placeholder="Clinic, dental, therapy, specialty..." />
            </label>
          </div>

          <label class="mt-4 grid gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#8a93a6]">
            Workflow to improve
            <textarea required name="workflow" class="min-h-28 w-full rounded-md border border-[#1c2333] bg-[#0c111c] px-3.5 py-3 text-[14px] text-[#f5f7fb] outline-none transition placeholder:text-[#5e6678] focus:border-[#67e8f9]/60 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#67e8f9]/15" placeholder="Patient intake, scheduling requests, reminders, forms, billing questions, portal messages..."></textarea>
          </label>

          <label class="mt-4 grid gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#8a93a6]">
            Monthly requests / appointments / messages
            <input name="volume" class="h-11 w-full rounded-md border border-[#1c2333] bg-[#0c111c] px-3.5 text-[14px] text-[#f5f7fb] outline-none transition placeholder:text-[#5e6678] focus:border-[#67e8f9]/60 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#67e8f9]/15" placeholder="e.g. 1,500 portal messages / month" />
          </label>

          <button type="submit" class="group mt-6 inline-flex h-12 w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[#22d3ee] px-7 text-[13px] font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#07090f] transition hover:bg-[#67e8f9]">
            Send healthcare workflow
            <Send class="ml-2 h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-0.5" />
          </button>
          <p id="healthcare-form-status" class="mt-3 text-center text-[12px] text-[#5e6678]">
            Prefer email? {brandEmail}
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-[#1c2333] bg-[#07090f] py-14">
    <div class={`${CONTAINER} flex flex-col justify-between gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-center`}>
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <img src="/favicon-96x96.png" alt="" width="30" height="30" class="rounded-md" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold">Tactas AI</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-sm text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-[#8a93a6]">
          Custom AI systems that support healthcare intake, scheduling, admin, and operations workflows.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-5 text-[12px] text-[#5e6678]">
        <a href="/" class="transition hover:text-[#c8d0de]">Home</a>
        <a href="/about" class="transition hover:text-[#c8d0de]">About</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="transition hover:text-[#c8d0de]">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="transition hover:text-[#c8d0de]">Terms</a>
        <a href={siteUrl} class="transition hover:text-[#c8d0de]">{siteUrl.replace(/^https?:\/\//, "")}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</div>

<script define:vars={{ brandEmail }} is:inline>
  const healthcareForm = document.getElementById("healthcare-inquiry-form");
  const healthcareStatus = document.getElementById("healthcare-form-status");
  healthcareForm?.addEventListener("submit", (event) => {
    event.preventDefault();
    const form = new FormData(healthcareForm);
    const organization = String(form.get("organization") || "").trim() || "Healthcare organization";
    const subject = encodeURIComponent(`Healthcare workflow inquiry - ${organization}`);
    const body = encodeURIComponent(
      [
        `Name: ${String(form.get("name") || "")}`,
        `Work email: ${String(form.get("email") || "")}`,
        `Organization: ${String(form.get("organization") || "")}`,
        `Care setting: ${String(form.get("setting") || "")}`,
        "",
        "Workflow to improve:",
        String(form.get("workflow") || ""),
        "",
        "Monthly requests / appointments / messages:",
        String(form.get("volume") || ""),
      ].join("\n"),
    );
    if (healthcareStatus) {
      healthcareStatus.textContent = "Opening your email client with the workflow details.";
    }
    window.location.href = `mailto:${brandEmail}?subject=${subject}&body=${body}`;
  });
</script>
